    <item>
      <title>英国发行 2040 年债券，寻求在初步协议成功的基础上再接再厉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/uk-offers-2040-bonds-seeking-to-build-on-success-of-initial-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国将于周二通过银行发售 2040 年到期的债券，希望借此巩固此前发售的成功以及本月早些时候遭遇抛售后需求的复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/uk-offers-2040-bonds-seeking-to-build-on-success-of-initial-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:19:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯试图介入汽车金融事件，英国银行股飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/uk-banks-soar-as-reeves-looks-to-intervene-in-motor-finance-saga</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 试图介入最高法院审理的一起具有里程碑意义的案件，该案件涉及英国各大银行汽车金融业务的历史做法。随后，英国各大银行的股价飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/uk-banks-soar-as-reeves-looks-to-intervene-in-motor-finance-saga</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:10:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行称特朗普的温和政策将刺激股市落后者反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/bofa-says-benign-trump-policies-to-spark-rally-in-stock-laggards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行公司的一项调查显示，有早期迹象表明，投资者正准备迎接股市落后者的反弹，因为投资者押注美国总统唐纳德·特朗普可能会对全球贸易采取比人们担心的更为温和的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/bofa-says-benign-trump-policies-to-spark-rally-in-stock-laggards</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:10:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度证券交易委员会考虑采取措施遏制 IPO 股票“黑市”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/india-s-sebi-mulls-steps-to-curb-black-market-in-ipo-shares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度证券市场监管机构正在考虑采取措施，使首次公开募股的交易正式化，其中竞标已结束，但股票尚未上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/india-s-sebi-mulls-steps-to-curb-black-market-in-ipo-shares</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:09:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国自五月以来首次通过银行发售债券，被抢购一空</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/france-offers-bonds-via-banks-for-first-time-in-eight-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国新政府试图获得足够的支持来通过急需的预算，该国约八个月以来首次银团债券发售获得了大量投资者的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/france-offers-bonds-via-banks-for-first-time-in-eight-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 09:02:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市的关税豁免可能只是暂时的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/chinese-stocks-tariff-reprieve-is-likely-to-be-only-temporary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统上任第一天没有宣布对中国征收任何关税，这给中国股市带来了惊喜。但投资者并没有因此而高枕无忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/chinese-stocks-tariff-reprieve-is-likely-to-be-only-temporary</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 08:58:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场担心美国液化天然气计划收紧，欧洲天然气价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/european-gas-prices-swing-as-trump-lifts-ban-on-new-lng-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气价格上涨，交易商认为鉴于美国计划增加出口，欧洲天然气供应可能再紧张一年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/european-gas-prices-swing-as-trump-lifts-ban-on-new-lng-exports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 07:32:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新世界银行承诺提供 150 亿美元贷款，利润率受限，压力加大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/new-world-offers-15-billion-for-loan-collateral-as-stress-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着香港房地产开发商新世界发展有限公司将其部分最有价值的资产抵押以获得贷款，且券商不再为该公司的股票和债券提供融资，该公司信贷压力的迹象正在加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/new-world-offers-15-billion-for-loan-collateral-as-stress-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 02:21:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国暂停加征关税缓解通胀担忧 美国债券价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/treasuries-rally-on-first-trading-day-under-trump-presidency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统暂时没有对中国征收特定关税，因市场对唐纳德·特朗普政策将加剧通胀的担忧有所缓解，美国国债价格出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/treasuries-rally-on-first-trading-day-under-trump-presidency</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 00:25:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
